Here's how to release Hailo:

# Get custom build tools:

    # With fixes to override MakeMaker.pm
    git clone git://github.com/avar/dist-zilla.git

# Build Hailo

    # Build Hailo, see Hailo-* for what'll be released
    perl -I ~/g/dist-zilla/lib $(which dzil) build
    # Test it
    perl -I ~/g/dist-zilla/lib $(which dzil) test

# Release

    # Now increment version in dist.ini (but don't commit) and:
    perl -I ~/g/dist-zilla/lib $(which dzil) release

    # Git::* plugins will automatically commit dist.ini / Changes and tag the release
    git push && git push --tags

